14:30.364 --> 14:31.666
In terms of digital projects?

14:31.726 --> 14:32.707
In terms of digital projects.

14:32.888 --> 14:32.968
Yes.

14:33.108 --> 14:36.353
There are a couple that are going on at the moment.

14:36.453 --> 14:43.143
One is MESL, and that's a combination of museums and libraries across the country.

14:43.163 --> 14:44.125
How do you spell it?

14:44.145 --> 14:45.447
M-E-S-L.

14:45.467 --> 14:48.351
It's an acronym.

14:56.701 --> 14:58.002
I was about to ask you.

14:58.022 --> 14:58.443
Oh.

14:58.463 --> 15:00.244
I love, I mean, I love tons of things.

