43:11.728 --> 43:13.890
The difficulty in our work is

43:14.242 --> 43:24.717
is keeping a constant thread going so that you're not developing a collection that is a roadmap of fads that start and stop along the way.

43:24.777 --> 43:25.418
Has that happened?

43:25.918 --> 43:26.719
It can happen.

43:26.739 --> 43:35.231
